#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:550
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also use the <mousebutton>wheel</mousebutton> mouse to scroll up and "
"down."
msgstr ""
"También puede utilizar la <mousebutton>rueda</mousebutton> del ratón para "
"desplazarse arriba y abajo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:552
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the merge output editor you can also use the other keys for editing. You "
